1. *Dolazio* je tu već neko vreme. (He had been coming here for some time.)
2. On je *dolazio* svakog dana. (He was coming every day.)
3. *Dolazila* je posetilaca iz cijelog sveta. (Visitors were coming from all over the world.)
4. Znao je da će *dolaziti* gosti. (He knew that the guests would come.)
5. Ona me je obavestila da će *dolaziti*. (She informed me that she would be coming.)
6. Da li će *dolaziti* na proslavu? (Will they be coming to the celebration?)